<p>
  <span class="nym">Petra</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym">Fem. of <a class="nym" href="Peter">Peter</a>.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
  
<div class="def">
  <p><i>Petra</i> itself is quite rare; most of the feminine forms of this name either derive from French <i>Pierre</i>, usually with a diminutive suffix, or from the derivative <a class="nym" href="Petronilla">Petronilla</a>, q.v.</p>
  
  


